"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"karaoke\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of all, what kept the Philippines close to Hoffman's heart was the strong sense of family.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999768079, \"rank\": 2.283053227208514e-11, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 1668, \"end\": 1675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the strong sense\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After discovering her international potential, Hoffman decided to link up with Philippine Amateur Track and Field Association (PATAFA), then led by former Philippine Sports Commission chairman Philip Ella Juico.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1764, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Sports_Commission\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippine Sports Commission\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine