ine colors\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By July 2024, the 25-year-old Hoffman made history again by qualifying for the 2024 Paris Olympics, earning just enough points in the world rankings to reach the cutoff mark in the women's 400m hurdles.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3198, \"end\": 3205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3266}, {\"ngram\": \"just enough points\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3294}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"the cutoff mark\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3341}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 400m hurdles\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am one of the only 400 [female] hurdlers to, like ever\\u2026 make it to the Olympics,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only 400 [female] hurdlers\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3415}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I am only the second ever [from the Philippines].\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3512, \"end\": 3523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999768079, \"rank\": 2.283053227208514e-11, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I feel there is like a lot of history to be made.\\\"\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think we are definitely getting better and better every year,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, coming off Hidilyn Diaz's gold medal [in the Tokyo Olympics], I think that just inspired the country, too.\\\"\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3684, \"end\": 3696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hidilyn_Diaz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hidilyn Diaz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hidilyn_Diaz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hidilyn_Diaz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in the small, sleepy town of Haymarket, Hoffman first competed in running during her elementary school days, where she would participate in events like the 5km run.\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3822, \"end\": 3831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theatre_Royal_Haymarket\", \"score\": 0.8676926103063028, \"rank\": 0.15248186756694762, \"text\": \"Haymarket\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q24354\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theatre_Royal_Haymarket\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theatre_Royal_Haymarket\"}, {\"begin\": 3833, \"end\": 3840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the small, sleepy town\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3818}, {\"ngram\": \"her elementary school days\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5km run\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 13 years old, Hoffman then decided to shift to hurdling, which she recalled loving right at the moment she leapt her first obstacle.\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 4094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3976, \"end\": 3983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hurdling\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4017}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4064}, {\"ngram\": \"her first obstacle\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Battlefield High School, she was named a New Balance Nationals All-American, winning the state championship in the 4x400m relay and finishing fourth in the women's 400m hurdles in 2017.\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4099, \"end\": 4110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battlefield\", \"score\": 0.9999999979468157, \"rank\": 2.0531998649800828e-09, \"text\": \"Battlefield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battlefield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battlefield\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a New Balance Nationals\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4161}, {\"ngram\": \"the state championship\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4206}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x400m relay\", \"from\": 4210, \"to\": 4226}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 400m hurdles\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 5-foot-6 athlete also played volleyball, but was likewise relentless in academics, graduating summa cum laude.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4384, \"end\": 4399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin_honors\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"summa cum laude\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin_honors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin_honors\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 5-foot-6 athlete\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4306}, {\"ngram\": \"volleyball\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4329}, {\"ngram\": \"academics\", \"from\": 4362, \"to\": 4371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heading into college, Hoffman had two choices - Harvard University over in the northeast, or Duke University, about 260 miles away southwest of her hometown.\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4424, \"end\": 4431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}, {\"begin\": 4495, \"end\": 4510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duke_University\", \"score\": 0.9999280581741615, \"rank\": 6.0757657150352656e-05, \"text\": \"Duke University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duke_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duke_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4422}, {\"ngram\": \"two choices\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4447}, {\"ngram\": \"Harvard University\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"the northeast\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4490}, {\"ngram\": \"her hometown\", \"from\": 4546, \"to\": 4558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a really tough decision for me because they are both great universities.\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really tough decision\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4592}, {\"ngram\": \"great universities\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew I would get a great education, get good degrees,\\\" recalled Hoffman.\", \"from\": 4642, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4708, \"end\": 4715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great education\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4678}, {\"ngram\": \"good degrees\", \"from\": 4684, \"to\": 4696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it came down to where I felt more at home.\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, who I vibed with, the ones who gave me a good feeling, which team felt like family.\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4802}, {\"ngram\": \"a good feeling\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4829}, {\"ngram\": \"team\", \"from\": 4837, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I just fell in love with the Duke track team.\\\"\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 4910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4883}, {\"ngram\": \"the Duke track team\", \"from\": 4889, \"to\": 4908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking up evolutionary anthropology with the intention of taking up medicine afterwards, Hoffman made her mark with the prestigious sporting program under the tutelage of coach Mark Mueller, who coaches her up to this day.\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 5134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5001, \"end\": 5008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.4151224113878787e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}, {\"begin\": 5089, \"end\": 5101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Mueller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mark Mueller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Mueller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Mueller\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"evolutionary anthropology\", \"from\": 4922, \"to\": 4947}, {\"ngram\": \"the intention\", \"from\": 4953, \"to\": 4966}, {\"ngram\": \"medicine\", \"from\": 4980, \"to\": 4988}, {\"ngram\": \"her mark\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5022}, {\"ngram\": \"the prestigious sporting program\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"the tutelage\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5079}, {\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was named to several All-Atlantic Coast Conference (ACC) First and Second Teams and was hailed as part of the US Track and Field and Cross Country Coaches Association (USTFCCCA) All-America First Team in the 2021 season.\", \"from\": 5136, \"to\": 5360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5192, \"end\": 5195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlantic_Coast_Conference\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.5870730045164886e-17, \"text\": \"ACC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlantic_Coast_Conference\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlantic_Coast_Conference\"}, {\"begin\": 5273, \"end\": 5286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cross_country_running\", \"score\": 0.9999959275502239, \"rank\":